Value switch_num (\d+)
Value pid (\S+)
Value serial_number (\S+)
Value cloud_id (\S+)
Value mac_address (\S+)
Value migration_status (\S+)
Value mode (\S+)

Start
  ^Switch\s+Serial\s+Migration\s*$$
  ^Num\s+PID\s+Number\s+Cloud ID\s+Mac Address\s+Status\s+Mode\s*$$
  ^-+\s*$$
  ^${switch_num}\s+${pid}\s+${serial_number}\s+${cloud_id}\s+${mac_address}\s+${migration_status}\s+${mode}\s*$$ -> Record
